==English==

{{rank|door|round|kind|278|form|hundred|believe|white}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# The [[shape]] or visible structure of a thing or person.
# A thing that gives shape to other things as in a [[mold]].
# An order of doing things, as in religious [[ritual]].
# A blank document or [[template]] to be filled in by the user.
# {{grammar}} A grouping of words which maintain grammatical [[context]] in different usages.
# Characteristics not involving atomic components.

====Synonyms====
*[[figure]], used when discussing people, not animals
*[[shape]], used on animals and on persons

